-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:3.4":{"pli":"phaladānassidaṁ phalaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap508:4.1":{"pli":"Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:4.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:4.3":{"pli":"viharāmi anāsavo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap508:5.1":{"pli":"Svāgataṁ vata me āsi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:5.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:5.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap508:6.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:6.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap508:6.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap508:7.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā mātuluṅgaphaladāyako thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap508:8.1":{"pli":"Mātuluṅgaphaladāyakattherassāpadānaṁ chaṭṭhaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"tha-ap509":{"tha-ap509:0.1":{"pli":"Therāpadāna ","html":"<article id='tha-ap509'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"tha-ap509:0.2":{"pli":"Kaṇikāravagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"tha-ap509:0.3":{"pli":"7 Ajeliphaladāyakattheraapadāna ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"tha-ap509:1.1":{"pli":"“Ajjuno nāma sambuddho, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:1.2":{"pli":"himavante vasī tadā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:1.3":{"pli":"Caraṇena ca sampanno, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:1.4":{"pli":"samādhikusalo muni. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap509:2.1":{"pli":"Kumbhamattaṁ gahetvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:2.2":{"pli":"ajeliṁ jīvajīvakaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:2.3":{"pli":"Chattapaṇṇaṁ gahetvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:2.4":{"pli":"adāsiṁ satthuno ahaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap509:3.1":{"pli":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:3.2":{"pli":"yaṁ phalaṁ adadiṁ tadā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:3.3":{"pli":"Duggatiṁ nābhijānāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:3.4":{"pli":"phaladānassidaṁ phalaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap509:4.1":{"pli":"Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:4.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:4.3":{"pli":"viharāmi anāsavo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap509:5.1":{"pli":"Svāgataṁ vata me āsi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:5.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:5.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap509:6.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:6.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap509:6.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap509:7.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā ajeliphaladāyako thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap509:8.1":{"pli":"Ajeliphaladāyakattherassāpadānaṁ sattamaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"tha-ap51":{"tha-ap51:0.1":{"pli":"Therāpadāna ","html":"<article id='tha-ap51'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"tha-ap51:0.2":{"pli":"Upālivagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"tha-ap51:0.3":{"pli":"Subhaddattheraapadāna ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"tha-ap51:1.1":{"pli":"“Padumuttaro lokavidū, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:1.2":{"pli":"āhutīnaṁ paṭiggaho; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:1.3":{"pli":"Janataṁ uddharitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:1.4":{"pli":"nibbāyati mahāyaso. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:2.1":{"pli":"Nibbāyante ca sambuddhe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:2.2":{"pli":"dasasahassi kampatha; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:2.3":{"pli":"Janakāyo mahā āsi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:2.4":{"pli":"devā sannipatuṁ tadā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:3.1":{"pli":"Candanaṁ pūrayitvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:3.2":{"pli":"tagarāmallikāhi ca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:3.3":{"pli":"Haṭṭho haṭṭhena cittena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:3.4":{"pli":"āropayiṁ naruttamaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:4.1":{"pli":"Mama saṅkappamaññāya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:4.2":{"pli":"satthā loke anuttaro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:4.3":{"pli":"Nipannakova sambuddho, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:4.4":{"pli":"imā gāthā abhāsatha. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:5.1":{"pli":"‘Yo me pacchimake kāle, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:5.2":{"pli":"gandhamālena chādayi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:5.3":{"pli":"Tamahaṁ kittayissāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:5.4":{"pli":"suṇātha mama bhāsato. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:6.1":{"pli":"Ito cuto ayaṁ poso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:6.2":{"pli":"tusitakāyaṁ gamissati; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:6.3":{"pli":"Tattha rajjaṁ karitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:6.4":{"pli":"nimmānaṁ so gamissati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:7.1":{"pli":"Eteneva upāyena, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:7.2":{"pli":"datvā mālaṁ varuttamaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:7.3":{"pli":"Sakakammābhiraddho so, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:7.4":{"pli":"sampattiṁ anubhossati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:8.1":{"pli":"Punāpi tusite kāye, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:8.2":{"pli":"nibbattissatiyaṁ naro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:8.3":{"pli":"Tamhā kāyā cavitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:8.4":{"pli":"manussattaṁ gamissati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:9.1":{"pli":"Sakyaputto mahānāgo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:9.2":{"pli":"aggo loke sadevake; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:9.3":{"pli":"Bodhayitvā bahū satte, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:9.4":{"pli":"nibbāyissati cakkhumā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:10.1":{"pli":"Tadā sopagato santo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:10.2":{"pli":"sukkamūlena codito; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:10.3":{"pli":"Upasaṅkamma sambuddhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:10.4":{"pli":"pañhaṁ pucchissati tadā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap51:11.1":{"pli":"Hāsayitvāna sambuddho, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:11.2":{"pli":"sabbaññū lokanāyako; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap51:11.3":{"pli":"Puññakammaṁ pa